ge</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/fullscreenerror_event\"><code>fullscreenerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/gotpointercapture_event\"><code>gotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/mssitemodejumplistitemremoved_event\"><code>mssitemodejumplistitemremoved</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/msthumbnailclick_event\"><code>msthumbnailclick</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/paste_event\"><code>paste</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointercancel_event\"><code>pointercancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerdown_event\"><code>pointerdown</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerenter_event\"><code>pointerenter</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerleave_event\"><code>pointerleave</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerlockchange_event\"><code>pointerlockchange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerlockerror_event\"><code>pointerlockerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointermove_event\"><code>pointermove</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerout_event\"><code>pointerout</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerover_event\"><code>pointerover</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\"><code>readystatechange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>drop</code></strong> event is fired when an element or text selection is dropped on a valid drop target.</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Bubbles</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Cancelable</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default action</th>\n      <td>Varies</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Interface</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DragEvent\"><code>DragEvent</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Event handler property</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\" title=\"ondrop\"><code>ondrop</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"a_minimal_drag_and_drop_example","title":"A minimal drag and drop example","isH3":true,"content":"<p>In this example, we have a draggable element inside a container. Try grabbing the element, dragging it over the other container, and then releasing it.</p>\n<p>We use three event handlers here:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>in the <code>dragstart</code> event handler, we get a reference to the element that the user dragged</li>\n  <li>in the <code>dragover</code> event handler for the target container, we call <code>event.preventDefault()</code>, which enables it to receive <code>drop</code> events.</li>\n  <li>in the <code>drop</code> event handler for the drop zone, we handle moving the draggable element from the original container to the drop zone.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a more complete example of drag and drop, see the page for the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drag_event\"><code>drag</code></a> event.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dropzone<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>draggable<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">draggable</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    This div is draggable\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dropzone<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* Prevent the user selecting text in the example */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">user-select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#draggable</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.dropzone</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blueviolet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> dragged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragstart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// store a ref. on the dragged elem</span>\n  dragged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragover\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// prevent default to allow drop</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"drop\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// prevent default action (open as link for some elements)</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// move dragged element to the selected drop target</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>className <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    dragged<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dragged<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dragged<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"A minimal drag and drop example sample\" id=\"frame_a_minimal_drag_and_drop_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drop_event/_sample_.a_minimal_drag_and_drop_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/dnd.html#event-dnd-drop","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Document.drop_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Document.drop_event","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drop_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Other drag and drop events:\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drag_event\" title=\"drag\"><code>drag</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragstart_event\" title=\"dragstart\"><code>dragstart</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragend_event\" title=\"dragend\"><code>dragend</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragover_event\" title=\"dragover\"><code>dragover</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragenter_event\" title=\"dragenter\"><code>dragenter</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragleave_event\" title=\"dragleave\"><code>dragleave</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>This event on other targets:\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>: <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>drop</code></a> event</li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\" title=\"drop\"><code>drop</code></a> event</li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a>: <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>drop</code></a> event</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The drop event is fired when an element or text selection is dropped on a valid drop target.","popularity":0.0022,"modified":"2022-05-31T04:29:22.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"drop","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document: drop イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"drop","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/document/drop_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/document/drop_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/37f38ac4b337174d6b7ccf3fc08b1ac66c5a9fcd","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drop_event","title":"Document: drop event"}],"pageTitle":"Document: drop event - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing"